[Also see Ebola dashboard https://who.maps.arcgis.com/apps/opsdashboard/index.html#/e70c3804f6044652bc37cce7d8fcef6c

Ebola DRC Kivu 2018 Dashboard reports 9 new cases on 5 Jul 2019, making 60 cases so far this week, 272 in the past 21 days, and 2398 since the outbreak began on 1 Aug 2018. Out of 18 800 contacts, 2200 are going untraced. There is a discrepancy in case numbers, 2389 vs 2398, most likely due to date difference in tally being taken.

